name: Dedos del Diablo
description:
The monstrous finger-like tentacles begin to secrete rotten-flesh-scented slime filled with the fungus's spores. It makes a sound similar to an erupting volcano in the adult stage of the fungus. Life time is about 200 years.

As the story goes the devil himself was the creator of this creature It was first seen in 1769 in New Zealand and Australia and in some mysterious way it is invading the north of Spain today.
